EXPERT LEVEL
In this level we will also need a client(client.py) which, if it is ran it will show the outputs as if we were
requesting them from the browser. In this report we will get the output from the browser, but same dictionary will be
obtained by running the client (the client will show all the outputs that I introduced).
All exceptions which were controlled in medium and basic level are also held here, like for example change of order of
the variables or trying to break the program like introducing letters where only numbers are accepted.
In all the directions used parameter 'json=1' is included; with this, instead of a 'nice' html file, we will obtain
a json, which if we request to see the code we will see a dictionary (on a single line)
